1. *Spusti* se sa stolice i pridruži se nama. (Get off the chair and join us.)
2. Doktor je *spustio* dijagnozu. (The doctor lowered the diagnosis.)
3. On je *spustio* ruke dole. (He lowered his hands down.)
4. Ona je *spustila* glas. (She lowered her voice.)
5. *Spustiću* te kod kuće. (I'll drop you off at home.)
6. *Spusti* se niz liticu! (Come down the cliff!)
7. On je *spustio* oči na pod. (He lowered his eyes to the ground.)